🔷 1️⃣ CSS Transitions in React (Basic Way)

```jsx
function Box() {
  return (
    <div className="box"></div>
  );
}
```

```css
.box {
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  background: blue;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.box:hover {
  transform: scale(1.2);
}
```

📌 Simple
📌 Good for small effects

