```

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 3️⃣ React Motion (Older Library)

📌 Physics-based animation library

Install:

```bash
npm install react-motion
```

Example:

```jsx
import { Motion, spring } from "react-motion";

<Motion defaultStyle={{ x: 0 }} style={{ x: spring(100) }}>
  {value => <div style={{ transform: `translateX(${value.x}px)` }} />}
</Motion>
```

✔ Smooth spring animation
❌ Less commonly used today

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 4️⃣ React Spring (Modern & Powerful)

📌 Physics-based animation
📌 Very flexible

Install:

```bash
npm install @react-spring/web
```

Example:

```jsx
import { useSpring, animated } from "@react-spring/web";

function Fade() {
  const styles = useSpring({
    from: { opacity: 0 },
    to: { opacity: 1 }
  });

  return <animated.div style={styles}>Hello</animated.div>;
}
```

✔ Great for complex animations
✔ Gesture support

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 5️⃣ Framer Motion (Most Popular ⭐)

📌 Very easy
📌 Powerful
📌 Used in production apps

Install:

```bash
npm install framer-motion
```

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Basic Animation Example

```jsx
import { motion } from "framer-motion";

function Box() {
  return (
    <motion.div
      animate={{ x: 100 }}
      transition={{ duration: 0.5 }}
    >
      Move Me
    </motion.div>
  );
}
```

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Hover & Tap Animations

```jsx
<motion.button
  whileHover={{ scale: 1.1 }}
  whileTap={{ scale: 0.9 }}
>
  Click Me
</motion.button>
```

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Page Transition Animation

```jsx
<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0 }}
  animate={{ opacity: 1 }}
  exit={{ opacity: 0 }}
>
  Page Content
</motion.div>
```

✔ Great for routing animations

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 Animation with State

```jsx
const [isOpen, setIsOpen] = useState(false);

<motion.div
  animate={{ height: isOpen ? 200 : 100 }}
/>
```

📌 State controls animation

