🆚 React Motion vs React Spring vs Framer Motion

| Library       | Ease        | Power     | Popularity |
| ------------- | ----------- | --------- | ---------- |
| React Motion  | Medium      | Good      | Low        |
| React Spring  | Medium      | Very High | Medium     |
| Framer Motion | Very Easy ⭐ | High      | Very High  |

📌 Recommended: **Framer Motion**

